nodes.text: The Dactyl was a model of starship manufactured by Rendili StarDrive. One was once used by Jaina Solo, Zekk and Jagged Fel during their hunt for Alema Rar.

Though far less maneuverable than a YT-2400 light freighter, the Dactyl contained at least enough room for three private berths for crew members and enough space to store StealthXs. It was also equipped with two observation blisters, both several meters apart on opposite sides of the fuselage, and an intercom.
